<h1> "In High-Drama Parody, Will Ferrell Reveals 'Spoils Of Babylon'" </h1>
    <p>ARUN RATH, HOST: </p>
    <p>We'll take a look back now at a best-selling book from the '70s, one you might not remember: "The Spoils of Babylon," by Eric Jonrosh, the epic tale of the powerful yet scandalous Morehouse family. It was made into a television miniseries that never saw the light of day - until now.</p>
    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF TV SHOW, "THE SPOILS OF BABYLON")</p>
